    <j.0:dossier_title xml:lang="en">Proposal for a COUNCIL DECISION concerning the conclusion of an agreement between the European Community and the Republic of Iceland and the Kingdom of Norway concerning the criteria and mechanisms for establishing the State responsible for examining a request for asylum lodged in a Member State or Iceland or Norway</j.0:dossier_title>
